      "title": "config 파일 import 테스트",
      "text": "%spark.pyspark\r\nimport boto3, os, sys\r\n\r\n# ── S3 → 로컬 다운로드 ────────────────────────────────────\r\ns3        \u003d boto3.client(\"s3\", endpoint_url\u003dos.environ.get(\"S3_ENDPOINT_URL\"))\r\nlocal_dir \u003d \"/tmp/kmon\"\r\nos.makedirs(local_dir, exist_ok\u003dTrue)\r\n\r\nfor f in [\"kmon_kslab_config.py\", \"kmon_kslab_pp_func.py\", \"kmon_kslab_utils.py\"]:\r\n    s3.download_file(\"quantum\", f\"data_folder/Intergrated_Schema/kmon/{f}\", f\"{local_dir}/{f}\")\r\n    print(f\"Downloaded: {f}\")\r\n\r\nsys.path.insert(0, local_dir)\r\n\r\nimport kmon_kslab_config\r\nimport kmon_kslab_pp_func\r\nimport kmon_kslab_utils\r\nprint(\"\u003d\u003d\u003d OK \u003d\u003d\u003d\")",
